quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  4,142,"Mazima Abannafunsi bakwenyakwenya Katonda, kale naye waakubakwenyakwenya, era bwebayimirira okusaala bayimirira lwabuwaze, nga bagenderera kulaga bantu era tebatendereza Katonda okugyako katono nnyo"
  4,143,"Ba nampa wengwa (wakati wa Bakkiriza na Bakafiiri) nga tebayinza kubalibwa ku bali oba ku bano, bulijjo omuntu Katonda gwabuza tayinza kumufunira kkubo. (lidda eri bulungamu)"
  4,144,"Abange mmwe abakkiriza temufuula nga abakafiiri mikwano gyammwe nfiira bulago nemuleka abakkiriza, mwandiyagadde okwewaako obujulizi obwolwatu ewa Katonda"
  4,145,"Mazima Abannanfusi bagenda kubeera ku mwaliiro ogusemberayo ddala wansi mu muliro, ate nga togenda kubafunira mutaasa"
  4,146,"Okugyako abo abeenenya, nebalongoosa, nebekwata ku Katonda, nga neddiini yaabwe bagikola kulwa Katonda yekka, abo nno bagenda kuba wamu nabakkiriza. Ate nga Katonda abakkiriza agenda kubawa empeera ensukkulumu"
  4,147,"Singa mwebaza Katonda, era nemukkiriza, ate olwo Katonda aliba ababonerereza lwaki! ate nga bulijjo Katonda mwebaza era mumanyi nnyo"
  4,148,"Katonda tayagala kwatuukiriza kigambo kibi (ku muntu) okugyako oyo aba alangiddwa obwereere, bulijjo Katonda awulira era amanyi nnyo"
  4,149,"Bwemwolesa ekirungi, oba nemukikweka, oba nemusonyiwa abayisizza obubi, mazima bulijjo Katonda alekera, muyinza nnyo"
  4,150,"Mazima abo abajeemera Katonda n’ababakabe, nebagezaako okwawula wakati wa Katonda n’ababakabe, era nebagamba nti tukkirizaako abamu abalala tetubakkiriza, nebaagala okuteekawo ekkubo wakati weebyo ebibiri, (babe nga mwebatambulira)"
  4,151,Abo nno beebatakkiriza abannamaddala. Era nga abakafiiri twabategekera ebibonerezo ebinyoomesa
  4,152,"Ate abo abakkiriza Katonda n'ababaka be nebatayawula wakati w’omu kubo, abo nno Katonda agenda kubawa empeera yaabwe, bulijjo Katonda musonyiyi wa kisa nnyo"